    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you want to play an RPG with your friends but don’t have 1000 hours to grind? You like complex card games, but don’t want to read a novel every time you see a new card? Wanna combo off so hard you might blow up yourself? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Well, <strong>Shuffle Quest</strong>’s got you covered! Shuffling up the complex strategy of <strong>card battlers</strong>, the endless replayability of <strong>roguelites</strong> and the untamed chaos of a <strong>co-op RPG</strong> is a sure-fire way to slay the princess, save the dragon and be back at the tavern before happy hour!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/5dd0747dd4be5eb92179166fc1b0dd2f.poster.avif?t=1733925843\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/5dd0747dd4be5eb92179166fc1b0dd2f.webm?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/5dd0747dd4be5eb92179166fc1b0dd2f.mp4?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/43deb3cdf03f87ae77c45d6e57e2202e.webp?t=1733925843\" width=275 height=59 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Take the role of a party of roguish adventurers in a quest to loot every corner of Boardia’s frontier!<strong> Play with your friends</strong> or <strong>manage the party</strong> all on your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/fa8f5d612c87efdd98f9812b1612d4a1.poster.avif?t=1733925843\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/fa8f5d612c87efdd98f9812b1612d4a1.webm?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/fa8f5d612c87efdd98f9812b1612d4a1.mp4?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/0a8099267267fa7817dfb1aaffb78cbb.webp?t=1733925843\" width=275 height=59 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each character in the game has strengths and weaknesses, but none can triumph on their own. <strong>Joining the power of four decks</strong> the combo potential is unlimited.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/f7d35603a4cb12eaf9171c3166437a10.poster.avif?t=1733925843\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/f7d35603a4cb12eaf9171c3166437a10.webm?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/f7d35603a4cb12eaf9171c3166437a10.mp4?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/485c4fdf8cda47455421c2dc23ff35a6.webp?t=1733925843\" width=275 height=59 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Boardia’s frontier is home to all sorts of outlandish folks, from trenchcoat stacking <strong>cowboy gobs</strong> to road hogs<strong> pork orcs</strong>, with no shortage of <strong>cupcake baking slimes</strong> in between.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/5e8e0f6e28da4eca457e527e126d7e94.poster.avif?t=1733925843\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/5e8e0f6e28da4eca457e527e126d7e94.webm?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/5e8e0f6e28da4eca457e527e126d7e94.mp4?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/f32bc0a1aade62e9fea34f57044498d9.webp?t=1733925843\" width=275 height=59 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  With over <strong>120 cards</strong>,<strong> 30 items</strong> and<strong> randomly generated maps</strong>, Shuffle Quest brings the most endless replayability of all endlessly replayable games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/4e0287ad95988667daf96d8130775ddb.poster.avif?t=1733925843\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/4e0287ad95988667daf96d8130775ddb.webm?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/4e0287ad95988667daf96d8130775ddb.mp4?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/fe3ba4ba844823043816b695c76c7d85.webp?t=1733925843\" width=275 height=59 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Throughout your adventures you’ll encounter some good old <strong>story events</strong> where you’ll have a choice. Will you <strong>ponder the orb</strong>,<strong> burn down the library</strong> or <strong>invite the evil guy to your B-day</strong>? It’s up to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/b1ef3b166d492b044c8ec152a2016f57.poster.avif?t=1733925843\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/b1ef3b166d492b044c8ec152a2016f57.webm?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192980/extras/b1ef3b166d492b044c8ec152a2016f57.mp4?t=1733925843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
